   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">
         <table id="table_qhs_l2m_lcc" class="- topic/table ">
            <tgroup cols="2" class="- topic/tgroup ">
               <colspec colname="c1" colnum="1" colwidth="1*" class="- topic/colspec "/>
               <colspec colname="c2" colnum="2" colwidth="1*" class="- topic/colspec "/>
               <tbody class="- topic/tbody ">
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry "/>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <note type="danger" id="note_ijy_l2m_lcc" class="- topic/note ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">
                              <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Danger of electric shock!</b> Contact with live  components
                                 poses a risk of serious injury or even death! <ul id="ul_ft1_42m_lcc" class="- topic/ul ">
                                 <li class="- topic/li ">Before starting work, switch off the electric power supply.
                                       Follow plant requirements for lockout tagout.</li>
                              </ul>
                           </p>
                        </note>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry "/>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <note type="danger" id="note_kln_42m_lcc" class="- topic/note ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">
                              <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Life threatening hazard due to a falling vertical carriage!</b>
                              The unsecured vertical carriage can fall down and cause serious injury
                              or even death! <ul id="ul_orr_p2m_lcc" class="- topic/ul ">
                                 <li class="- topic/li ">Always make sure that the safety bolts of the vertical carriage
                                    are properly installed before carrying out work on / near the
                                    carriage!</li>
                              </ul>
                           </p>
                        </note>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry "/>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <note type="warning" id="note_src_q2m_lcc" class="- topic/note ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">
                              <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Danger of injury from improperly performed maintenance!</b>
                              Improper maintenance can result in serious personal injury or material
                                 damage!<ul id="ul_mqs_r2m_lcc" class="- topic/ul ">
                                 <li class="- topic/li ">Before starting work, ensure that you have sufficient
                                    space!</li>
                                 <li class="- topic/li ">Handle open, sharp-edged components with care!</li>
                                 <li class="- topic/li ">Pay attention to cleanliness and orderliness at the place of
                                    work! Loose components and tools lying around are a potential
                                    cause of accidents!</li>
                                 <li class="- topic/li ">Install all components correctly. Observe the prescribed bolt
                                    tightening torques! Secure the bolts with bolt locking com-
                                    pound (e.g. Weicon AN 302-43 (blue)) “medium strength”!</li>
                                 <li class="- topic/li ">Secure components so that they cannot fall down or fall
                                    over!</li>
                                 <li class="- topic/li ">Operating elements of the Emergency Stop system must be freely
                                    accessible!</li>
                                 <li class="- topic/li ">Operate the machine only when all the safety devices, e.g.
                                    safety fence, light barriers and safety bolts are installed and
                                    fully functional!</li>
                              </ul>
                           </p>
                        </note>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry "/>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <note type="warning" id="note_zrm_w2m_lcc" class="- topic/note ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">
                              <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Risk of injury from stored pneumatic energy! </b> Pneumatic energy
                              may be stored in the machine that can lead to uncontrolled movements
                              of components and injuries!<ul id="ul_ldp_1fm_lcc" class="- topic/ul ">
                                 <li class="- topic/li ">Follow plant requirements for lockout tagout of the system.
                                    Only then start the maintenance work!</li>
                              </ul>
                           </p>
                        </note>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry "/>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <note type="warning" id="note_gr5_bfm_lcc" class="- topic/note ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">
                              <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b "> Danger of crushing!</b> There are several crushing points on the
                              machine that can cause injuries!<ul id="ul_upf_dfm_lcc" class="- topic/ul ">
                                 <li class="- topic/li ">Do not reach between the following points: <ul id="ul_jsx_dfm_lcc" class="- topic/ul ">
                                       <li class="- topic/li ">the vertical carriage and the steel housing</li>
                                       <li class="- topic/li ">the vertical carriage and the lifting mast</li>
                                       <li class="- topic/li ">the locking pins and the container</li>
                                       <li class="- topic/li ">the vertical carriage and the horizontal carriage!</li>
                                    </ul>
                                 </li>
                                 <li class="- topic/li ">No person is allowed inside the safety fence area when the
                                    machine is switched on!</li>
                              </ul>
                           </p>
                        </note>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry "/>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <note type="warning" id="note_gy2_jfm_lcc" class="- topic/note ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">
                              <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b "> Danger due to non-observance of the prohibition of transporting
                                 persons! </b>The MSK transfer system can pose a serious risk in the
                              event of non-compliance and/or circumvention of the prohibition of
                              trans- porting persons.<ul id="ul_rlk_kfm_lcc" class="- topic/ul ">
                                 <li class="- topic/li ">Only operate the transfer system when all safety devices are in
                                    place and in proper working condition, such as the programmed
                                    safety interlocks and physical E-Stops.</li>
                                 <li class="- topic/li ">No persons are allowed on the transfer system!</li>
                              </ul>
                           </p>
                        </note>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry "/>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <note type="warning" id="note_hvd_xfm_lcc" class="- topic/note ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">
                              <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b "> Risk of injury due to stored hydraulic energy! </b>Hydraulic
                              energy can be stored in the machine and cause the un- controlled
                              movement of components, which can lead to severe in- juries!<ul id="ul_wp3_yfm_lcc" class="- topic/ul ">
                                 <li class="- topic/li ">Switch off the MSK system, as explained in this document.</li>
                                 <li class="- topic/li ">Do not begin maintenance work until then!</li>
                              </ul>
                           </p>
                        </note>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry "/>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <note type="warning" id="note_bz5_zfm_lcc" class="- topic/note ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">Risk of injury due to laser radiation! Laser radiation can cause
                              serious eye damage.</p>
                           <ul id="ul_wy4_1gm_lcc" class="- topic/ul ">
                              <li class="- topic/li ">Do not look into the laser beam!</li>
                              <li class="- topic/li ">If it is not possible to avoid looking directly into the laser
                                 beam (e.g., during maintenance work), suitable eye protection must
                                 be worn.</li>
                           </ul>
                        </note>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry "/>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <note type="caution" id="note_trm_cgm_lcc" class="- topic/note ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">
                              <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Danger of electric shock! </b> Parts  of  the  machine  may
                                 still  be  live  even  when  the  emergency  stop  switch has been
                                 pressed! </p>
                           <ul id="ul_yxm_dgm_lcc" class="- topic/ul ">
                              <li class="- topic/li ">Do not touch live parts and leads!</li>
                              <li class="- topic/li ">Observe the instructions in the operating manual!</li>
                           </ul>
                        </note>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
               </tbody>
